SUMMARY:Frederick STEM Festival
DESCRIPTION:Location: Carroll Creek Amphitheater\, Frederick\, Maryland \nAdmission: Free \nThe 2nd Frederick STEM Carnival will occur on November 1st at Carroll Creek from 1 to 4 PM. The event builds on previous successes our Frederick events and offers a unique opportunity for Frederick residents to engage in STEM-related activities. At 2:30\, there will be a magic show\, and a juggler will walk around the event. We will have plenty of giveaways! \nThis event is being held with the Frederick Children’s Business Fair. \nOrganizations that have been invited to participate include: \nAstraZeneca \nBovine Intervention \nGoTeam Therapy Dogs \nLonza \nUrbana STEMM \nTheromfisher Scientific \nFrederick Community College Biology Department \nTexcell \nLanline Games (video game developer) \nHope4OurChildren Face Painter \nHood College \nBrunswick Robotics
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/frederick-stem-festival/
END:VEVENT
