SUMMARY:Game Your Future Conference
DESCRIPTION:This is the 4th annual Game Your Future is a conference\, an event organized by Maryland-regional developer groups at the Baltimore Convention Center.  It brings an experience similar to the Game Developers Conference (GDC) to the East Coast to fill the void of a more accessible event for our East Coast devs who want something near where they live.\n\nJoin us at the Game Your Future Conference\, where community\, creativity\, and career growth collide. Whether you’re a game developer\, esports enthusiast\, student\, or professional in a tangential industry\, this is your chance to upskill\, get inspired\, and build meaningful connections in an evolving job market. With top speakers\, hands-on learning\, and unmatched networking opportunities\, you’ll leave empowered to thrive in gaming—and beyond.\n\nTickets and info: https://www.game4good.gg/game-your-future-conference/\n\nIndie Showcase (submit your game to show at the conference): Submission Form
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/game-your-future-conference/
LOCATION:Baltimore Convention Center\, 1 W Pratt Street\, Baltimore\, MD\, 21201\, United States
END:VEVENT
