SUMMARY:Baltimore IGDA Year In Review 2025
DESCRIPTION:The Baltimore IGDA is finishing the year strong with our final event of the 2025 year\, ‘The Baltimore IGDA – Year In Review’. This event is being held at the Greene Turtle in Hunt Valley on Wednesday December 3rd from 6pm – 9pm. We will have speakers from all 15+ of the local game development companies on how their year was and a look toward the future for 2026. This event is normally one of the biggest and can’t miss events to network and check out what each of the local studios are doing. Please RSVP so we can get a headcount and share this can’t miss event! \n118 Shawan Rd Suite HH\, Hunt Valley\, MD 21030
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/baltimore-igda-year-in-review-2025/
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR